---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Mezcalómano" description="Privacy policy for Mezcalómano. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
  <Section class="policy-section" id="privacy">
    <h1 data-scroll class="fade-in">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="policy-content" data-scroll class="slide-up">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 2026</p>
      
      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>Mezcalómano ("we", "our", "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our website or use our services.</p>
      
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you provide directly, such as when you contact us through our contact form, subscribe to updates, or make a purchase. This may include your name, email address, mailing address, and any messages you send.</p>
      
      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to respond to your inquiries, process orders, send you updates about our products (with your consent), and improve our services.</p>
      
      <h2>Data Protection</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
      
      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use Google reCAPTCHA on our contact form to prevent spam. Your use of reCAPTCHA is subject to Google's Privacy Policy and Terms of Service.</p>
      
      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hola@mezcalomano.com">hola@mezcalomano.com</a>.</p>
      
      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
      
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hola@mezcalomano.com">hola@mezcalomano.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>

<script>
  import '../scripts/scroll-observer';
</script>

<style>
  .policy-section {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 4rem auto;
  }

  .policy-section h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--yellow-agave);
  }

  .policy-content {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .policy-content h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--yellow-agave);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .policy-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .policy-content a {
    color: var(--yellow-agave);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .policy-section {
      margin: 3rem auto;
    }

    .policy-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
